    <S id="026S1">
        <FORM kindOf="original">ka sitsuayan Tjimu ti Taupili; keman tua tsautsau, aya.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="original">ka siʦuajan cimu ti taupiɭi; kəman tua ʦauʦau, aja.</PHON>
        <FORM kindOf="standard">ka sicuayan Tjimu ti Taupili; keman tua caucau, aya.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="standard">ka siʦuajan ʦimu ti taupiɣi; kəman tua ʦauʦau, aja.</PHON>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="eng">Once upon a time there was a person of the Tjimu tribe called Taupili, who ate people, they say.</TRANSL>
