    <S id="026S2">
        <FORM kindOf="original">nu izua puaɫak sa ini pasemalavan tjai Taupili, sa keɫangi tu izua napuaɫak, vaiken a malap a aɫak, sa kani.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="original">nu izua puaʎak sa ini pasəmaɭavan cai taupiɭi, sa kəʎaŋi tu izua napuaʎak, vaikən a maɭap a aʎak, sa kani.</PHON>
        <FORM kindOf="standard">nu izua pualjak sa ini pasemalavan tjai Taupili, sa keljangi tu izua napualjak, vaiken a malap a aljak, sa kani.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="standard">nu izua puaʎak sa ini pasəmaɣavan ʦai taupiɣi, sa kəʎaŋi tu izua napuaʎak, vaikən a maɣap a aʎak, sa kani.</PHON>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="eng">If anyone had a child and didn’t tell Taupili, and (s)he got to know that someone had had a child, he would go and take the child and eat it.</TRANSL>
