    <S id="026S3">
        <FORM kindOf="original">saka nu qemtsi tua tsautsau, kanen a uta, aya tjautsikel.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="original">saka nu qəmʦi tua ʦauʦau, kanən a uta, aja cauʦikəɭ.</PHON>
        <FORM kindOf="standard">saka nu qemci tua caucau, kanen a uta, aya tjaucikel.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="standard">saka nu qəmʦi tua ʦauʦau, kanən a uta, aja ʦauʦikəɣ.</PHON>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="eng">When he killed people, they too were eaten, according to the story.</TRANSL>
